<paragraph id="B933EAD392ECD840524E4D0380915ACC" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F3D13D7C6D3EAC90987FBBAB166ABD4F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
CUBA. Prov. Oriente [
<normalizedToken id="CB94067FC83D7321074F7286B9282A93" originalValue="Holguín">Holguin</normalizedToken>
], 
<normalizedToken id="1858EDE3F2A69387BE3C308B66FC9CFA" originalValue="Río">Rio</normalizedToken>
Lebisa, Sierra de Cristal, 30 Dec. 1955, 
<emphasis id="D888E7B45BE931CA50E955AAE87BA43E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Bro. Alain &amp; M. 
<normalizedToken id="B81568202B7360951A1E216BE7ECA318" originalValue="López">Lopez</normalizedToken>
Figueiras
</emphasis>
4834 (holotype HAC, isotype US).
